OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRain clears
OL,6,Feastwards across southern areas,
OL,7,Fleaving clearer skies. Further showers
OL,8,Faffect the far north and northwest,
OL,9,Fbut much of northern UK stays dry,
